## Why this file points elsewhere

This repo is dual-tool (GitHub Copilot + Claude Code). To avoid drift, the canonical agent surface lives under `.github/`. Copilot auto-discovers it; Claude Code reads it through this pointer.

## Required reading order

1. `.github/instructions/README.md` — the agent operating manual (overlay over the `praxis` plugin)
2. `{{paths.project_context}}` — single documentation entry point
3. The relevant skill in `.github/skills/<skill>/SKILL.md` for the task at hand

